      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained green</strong> <strong>lentils</strong> to the pan with the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> and <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-9 min further or until thickened – this is your <strong>lentil bolognese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
